#: ''Due to complications she can't breast feed her baby and so she '''bottles''' him.''
# (''UK'' slang) Refrain from (doing something) because of a failure of nerve (abbr. of '''to [[bottle out]]''').
#: ''The rider '''bottled''' the big jump.''
# {{UK}} Hit (someone) with a bottle.

